London pt.2: Victoria & Albert Museum Solo Date

Today is my birthday 🥳 and my husband surprised me with a trip to the Getty Villa and a delicious meal at Inn of the Seventh Ray! Thankful for all of the love I’ve received this weekend and feeling incredibly lucky to have such amazing people in my life 💖

Happy birthday to my big sister, @kimdaugherty_ !! I’ve been so lucky to grow up with a sister like you to look up to! Intelligent, strong, caring, and a beauty to boot! Now you’re a role model to the coolest lil dude around! I can’t believe you’re a mama to a toddler, but here we are and you’re doing an amazing job! Love you, Kimmy!

Happy Valentine’s Day! These pictures were taken almost nine years apart. We were barely dating in the second image and now we’re a whole married couple!!! I’m so happy to be living life with you by my side. 💕
If I were a V:tM vampire, what would my clan be? 📷: @camricephoto
Got to attend an early screening of the #DnDMovie with two cuties!!! I absolutely loved it!!!

Happy birthday to the love of my life @nickkrein!!! He’s the most handsome, caring, and weird man I’ve ever met and I am beyond lucky to have him in my life. Even luckier to call him my husband. Happy birthday, my love!!!

Tuesday night, I got to head to @regalmovies to attend a screening of the @dungeonsanddragonsmovie for the second time, but this time in #4DX!!! @nickkrein came with me, rolled a massive d20, got a NATURAL 20(‼️), and won this @theopgames D&D Yahtzee for me!!! I can’t wait to see it again tonight with my D&D group ❤️🐉 @4dxusa @hasbro
Idk just I feel cute today ☺️

Happy birthday to my beautiful mama! (Who I am not that much taller than, it’s the shoes, I swear!!!) thank you for being a guiding light in my life and for sharing and encouraging artistic expression! I love you so much!

Saucy Wench Faire Day was a success! Thursday night I decided I didn’t have anything ~spicy~ enough to wear, but I did have fabric glue, microsuede, and a dream! So I made a skirt and top in a little over a day! I also added myself into the group pic bc I left early 🥲

Two photos, one year apart 💕
On Sunday, Nick and I celebrated our anniversary by renewing our vows at the Renaissance Faire! Shout out to @greatgats1 for taking the journey to do this silly and special anniversary for us!!! I can’t believe it’s been a year since I married the love of my life and man of my dreams. Time has flown by! It’s been amazing creating a home with him, building on our relationship, and simply loving each other. I am incredibly lucky to have met him and even luckier to be loved by him 🥰

⚖️justice⚔️
